column5: today i went on lake o it was a success. i caught my first laker and one  (V. small) salmon   that's my sister next to me. It was her first day on Lake O - she caught some fish. My Dad will post more about that later  yesterday I went out with frank and juli and dad. We saw vinnimon on the water.I caught one bow
Great stuff fella!!! Next time that father of yours brings you up North we'll have to get out for Lakers!
Congrats G-Man!!!  Had fun yesterday, too bad that darn wind kicked up so strong!  We'll see you soon.
That's just wicked G-Man     Congrats dude

thank's for the invite wayne. Next time you are in Cambridge, let us know! We have a spare room and you are welcome to stay over (and I did check with Dad  ) maybe we can all get out on Lake O for some fish
Great Report keep slaying them SBK
Little dude, you are an ace angler !!!  Awesome catch
Very nice fish! Congrats on your first laker
Wow! It looks as though you had a super time out there! Thanks for showing us the pictures.
you are welcome thanks for the comments
Way to go G-Man thats a great report and some nice fish. Thanks for sharing and congrats on the Laker. Keep it up and keep the post coming.
awesome!  Looks like you had fun!  Cheers!
